data.description: Here is your chance to get a turn key townhome in a high demand area of Blaine. This layout is great for entertaining friends and family with an open floor plan on the main level where the living room wraps into the kitchen/dining which flows out to the patio area for BBQ and grilling with outdoor seating and privacy. End unit townhome with extra parking spots right next to this unit makes it a breeze to host gatherings. You will not believe all the updates this place has and how well cared it has been taken care of. Granite countertops, under mount sink, painted cabinets, new laminate flooring, updated baths. The list goes on and on. Plus the convenience of this location is hard to beat. Minutes away from Target, grocery, retail, restaurants, parks, walking trails and lakes. Schedule your showing today!
